WEBVTT

00:00.869 --> 00:01.834
ng wrong.

00:08.296 --> 00:09.795
I'm sorry, Molly.

00:09.831 --> 00:11.197
I love you.

00:11.232 --> 00:12.264
That girl can really work up the tears.

00:12.300 --> 00:13.265
They're calling me

00:13.301 --> 00:14.800
"American Psycho."

00:14.836 --> 00:16.802
The press is all over my hotel.

00:16.838 --> 00:18.204
I'm going crazy.

00:18.239 --> 00:20.139
There's still the little matter

00:20.174 --> 00:22.074
of the 20,000 quid Kaley cost me.

00:22.110 --> 00:23.075
I'll get it.

00:23.111 --> 00:24.110
We have to find Molly's phone

00:24.145 --> 00:26.178
before someone else does.

00:26.214 --> 00:28.147
You want someone to pay
for what happened to your sister.

00:28.182 --> 00:30.983
- My family needs answers.
- Do you remember bagging up

00:31.019 --> 00:32.250
a stuffed monkey from Molly's room?

00:32.286 --> 00:34.449
Who gives a rat's arse
about a stuffed monkey?

00:34.484 --> 00:36.022
Whoever knicked it, that's who.

00:36.057 --> 00:37.890
The tabloids have just handed us

00:37.925 --> 00:39.025
an alternative suspect.

00:39.060 --> 00:40.339
Do you think
that professor knocked her up?

00:40.374 --> 00:41.455
Are you gonna go after him?

00:46.301 --> 00:47.300
Get away from my husband.

00:47.335 --> 00:49.268
Get away from him now.

